title: Beyond Your Limits - NLP Romania
description:
Hello, I found this recorded story on an NLP blog from Romania. The recording has a 

male romanian voice on it and tells the story of Luciano and his inner journey.

What's interesting is the combination of voice and sound that makes the story 

fascinating to listen. The recording sounds clean.

Format   : mp3
Bit rate : 192kbps
Duration : 8 min 30 sec

Enjoy and tell me what you think. No trolls please.
